726757f-a.title: Queens: Grand Avenue - Remsen Place
726757f-a.text:
Grand Avenue, north side, east from Remsen Place, showing
at the corner the Queens County Hotel of 1873. In 1891 B0reg's
Eatate still operated this place as a hotel. An ice cream parlor
was here in 1923, and a florist in 1934.
March 1923.
Euoene L. Armbruster Collection
